      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">常棣.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>常棣之華，鄂不韡韡。凡今之人，莫如兄弟。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The flowers of the cherry tree --
Are they not gorgeously displayed?
Of all the men in the world
There are none equal to brothers.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
