      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">常棣.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>兄弟鬩于牆，外禦其務。每有良朋，蒸也無戎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Brothers may quarrel inside the walls,
But they will oppose insult from without,
When friends, however good they may be,
Will not afford help.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__005__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
