      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">常棣.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>喪亂既平，既安且寧。雖有兄弟，不如友生。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When death and disorder are past,
And there are tranquillity and rest;
Although they have brothers,
Some reckon them not equal to friends.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__006__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
