      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.7</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">常棣.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>妻子好合，如鼓瑟琴。兄弟既翕，和樂且湛。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Loving union with wife and children
Is like the music of lutes;
But it is the accord of brothers
Which makes the harmony and happiness lasting.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__008__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
