      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.8</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">常棣.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>宜爾室家，樂爾妻孥。是究是圖，亶其然乎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>For the ordering of your family,
For your joy in your wife and children,
Examine this and study it; --
Will you not find that it is truly so?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
